description: A basic potion. Recovers 500 HP to the user.
name: Potion

description: Magical water. Restores 200 MP to the user.
name: Magic Water

description:
A rare, magical, herb. When ingested, removes almost all
types of negative status effects from the user.
name: Blessed Herb

description:
A mage spell adapted for non magic users! One time use.
Revives a KOed party member and heals them for 50%.
name: Spell Charge: Ressurection

description:
A crystal that can manipulate forcefields, with the 
correct type of power source.
name: Sage's Crystal (Unpowered)

description: An energy source required to power a Sage's Crystal.
name: Sage's Essence

description:
You told Sasha the truth of her allies. She was 
enraged. But, in her heart, she found peace.
name: Noble Confession

description:
With her last dying breaths, Sasha remained hopeful for
mankind's salvation. She donated her power to you.
name: Last Hope

description:
The old man fears that slimes will overrun his town
and kill everyone. An exaggeration, to say the least.
name: Concern

description:
The old man fears for his own safety. He fears the...
slimes? What?
name: Fear and Desperation

description:
A strange crystal. It is warm to the touch. You can
use this for crafting.
name: Shard of Fire

description: Your team won the snowball fight. What a celebration!
name: Number One

description:
You comforted the losing team. There is hope for
humanity after all.
name: Good Sport

description: Can I... Have your autograph, JK Howling??
name: Admiration

description:
Apparently "Chosen One" is codeword for a thief who 
takes money from innocent townspeople.
name: Suspicion

description:
You called the Memory Keeper a \N[10] in front of a
little girl. She will remember that. Way to go.
name: He's a what?

description:
Defeat the gods who rule the sky castle and save 
humanity from destruction.
name: Destroy the Sky Castle

description:
Legendary hero "Abel" has gone missing. He was last 
seen on the Oberon continent. Find him.
name: Find Hero: Abel

description: Free Luden Town from the evil spirits that haunt it.
name: Exorcise Luden

description:
A creature called a "mist dragon" is blocking the exit
of a cave. Capture it and bring it back for research.
name: Capture a Mist Dragon

description:
A citizen from Blackforge, Kendra, is missing. Reports 
suggest she was last seen hiking outside of town.
name: Find Citizen: Kendra

description:
An ancient mechanical being awakened in Allemantheia and 
destroyed a village. Investigate.
name: Investigate Anomaly

description:
A mushroom that adapted to resist toxic environments. 
Removes the "poison" status from the user.
name: Magnificent Mushroom

description:
A loaf of bread blessed with magic! Fully restores the
user's HP and MP.
name: Wonder Bread

description: Is this some kind of punishment?
name: The Cheesiest Cheese

description: A universal crafting material for making weapons.
name: Refined Steel

description: A universal crafting material for making weapons.
name: Refined Steel (Proxy)

description: Raw iron ore. Can be made into steel.
name: Iron Ore

description:
A spare key to Trevor's house. His house is located at
the south side of town. You can rest there if needed.
name: Trevor's Spare Key

description:
You want to return home? Corianne reminds you that
you're not alone in your struggle. How encouraging.
name: Encouragement

description:
You wish to learn to think for yourself? Corianne
supports you. She wants you to succeed inside and out.
name: Internal Change

description:
Kendra's sealed her soul into a crystal to protect everyone.
What does it do? Maybe you should take it to a Blacksmith.
name: Soul Crystal

description:
Teaches "Blaze Aura", a skill that only the Hero
class can learn.
name: Hero Technique: Blaze Aura

description:
A teleportation spell adapted for non magic users!
Strong enough to teleport one user to Blackforge.
name: Spell Charge: Teleport I

description:
You saved Kendra. She is in a better place now. 
Report to the Hero's Guild to turn this contract in.
name: Save Kendra (Complete)

description:
You saved Kendra, and possibly all of Blackforge. 
It had to be done, for the greater good.
name: For the Greater Good

description:
You saved Kendra and sent her home. You took the risk, 
and hopefully it will pay off in the end.
name: Mercy

description:
Your accomplishment has spread to the whole town, and 
has even inspired children to follow in your footsteps.
name: You're my hero!

description:
Magical fibers are typically used to create mage robes.
But, this one is... different. Try taking it to a blacksmith.
name: Root of Life

description: A raw gemstone with tremendous untapped power.
name: Unrefined Arkhalite

description:
A mythical jewel made from purifying the essence of
an Arkhalis spirit.
name: Arkhalite

description:
A canister designed to create light by gently burning
oil. Can be turned into a weak bomb.
name: Fuel Cell

description:
A small boulder. Capable of resisting small forces 
under its own weight.
name: Small Boulder

description:
A heavily damaged reactor that used to power an 
otherworldy android. It is mostly intact, however.
name: Purifier's Reactor

description:
You told Axis that you embraced the human ability to fail.
They approved this philosophy.
name: Opening Up

description:
You told Axis that you've remained faithful to Ciel
and your assigned mission. Axis thinks you're a fool.
name: Faith

description:
You controlled the source of the disturbance in
Allemantheia. Report to the Hero's Guild at once.
name: Investigate Anomaly (Complete)

description:
A potion that was chemically engineered to become
much more potent. Recovers 1,000 HP.
name: Super Potion

description: Condensed magical essence. Recovers 400 MP.
name: Magic Dew

description:
Legends say this magical fruit fell from the Sky 
Castle's gardens. Increases max HP by +100, permanently.
name: Sky Fruit

description: You gain this memory at the end of the game
name: Utopia (Memory)

description:
The Queen of Hazel city is rumored to have a Warp Core
in her castle. Convince her to sell it to you.
name: Bribe the Queen

description:
This map shows the location of a strange hidden castle.
It is located southwest of Blackforge. (Optional Dungeon)
name: Mysterious Coordinates

description:
Opals are worth a fortune in Hazel City. Use this to
bribe the queen to sell you the warp core sculpture.
name: Opal

description:
Use this note to gain access to Blackforge's Northmost
Castle.
name: Royal Entry Pass

description:
Name: Alvin Yakitori. Age: 21. 
Likes: Working at the theater. Dislikes: Megan.
name: Fake ID

description:
(605)–475–6968. A fake number for a fake ID. Fair 
trade, right?
name: Fake Number

description:
Obliterate all enemies with light damage, and restore
50% of the party's Max HP. Req: LV.30 Hero
name: Special: Excalibur

description:
Attack one enemy with light damage. Party's max HP will 
increase by +50% for 10 turns. Req: LV.30 Lancer.
name: Special: Hyper Thrust

description:
A mythical jewel made from purifying the essence of
an Arkhalis spirit.
name: Arkhalite (Proxy)

description:
Oblierate an enemy with augmentable damage. Party will
gain lifesteal on attacks for 8 turns. Req: LV.30 Blademaster.
name: Special: Bloodlust

description:
You'll need this to navigate through the dark tunnels
of the laboratory.
name: Weak Flashlight

description: Opens the center door of Hazel Lab B2.
name: Bio Lab Key

description:
Obliterate your enemies with dark damage. Party becomes
unable to die for 2 turns. Req: LV 30 Dark Mage.
name: Spellbook: Deathless

description:
You wanted to return home, but you've found already 
found home amongst new friends. You must fight for them.
name: Save the World

description:
Your friends know your malicious intentions, yet they
still stand by your side. Why?
name: Save the World

description:
Well... You have a working warp core in your possession
now. You still completed the mission. Give this to Hans.
name: Bribe the Queen (Complete)

description:
Nobody in Blackforge will know this warp core is fake. 
You'll surely be rewarded for handing it over though.
name: Fake Warp Core

description: Use this to review important controls.
name: Controls Guide

description:
The power of this artifact can break even the strongest
magical seals.
name: Etherea's Might

description: TESTING ONLY. Recovers 100 TP
name: Testing Potion

description: Tastes like grape juice. Recovers 15 TP to the user.
name: TP Potion

description:
Raises the user's magic DEF by +25% for 5 turns. 
Can stack up to 50%.
name: MDEF Potion

description:
Raises the user's ATK by +25% for 5 turns. Can stack up to
+50%.
name: ATK Potion

description:
Teaches "Fire Break Aura". ALL battlers will take 150%
fire damage while this aura is active. REQ: Dark Mage LV. 14.
name: Spellbook: Fire Break Aura

description:
Teaches "Ice Break Aura". ALL battlers will take 150%
ice damage while this aura is active. REQ: Dark Mage LV. 12
name: Spellbook: Ice Break Aura

description:
Teaches "Thunder Break Aura". ALL battlers will take 150%
thunder damage while this aura is active. REQ: Dark Mage LV. 22.
name: Spellbook: Thunder Break Aura

description:
A spicy herb that grows near volcanoes. Cures the
"frozen" status.
name: Pyro Herb

description: A soul crystal that was shaped by the power of bravery.
name: Maxim's Bravery

description: A soul crystal that was shaped by the power of wisdom.
name: Artea's Wisdom

description: A soul crystal that was shaped by the power of love.
name: Hina's Beauty

description: A soul crystal that was shaped by the power of jubilance.
name: Gus' Joy

description:
You've become extremely close to Arden, Cecilia, 
and Lia.
name: Family

description: 像是某人亲手缝制的针织外套，依稀可以见到一些线头...
name: 新的针织外套

description: 据说真的很快乐
name: 肥宅快乐水

description: 某个神秘的人物举办了一个神秘的活动，只要拥有入场券，全场酒水都免费！
name: 神秘活动入场券

description: NightClub神秘活动专用筹码，可以兑换奖品哦
name: 筹码
